[normal]The reduction in ITB has been 
[normal]in part offset by 
[normal]a wide range of
[normal] 
[normal]DfT
[normal] funding competitions. 
[normal]However, this approach to funding 
[normal]runs the risk of undermining Government’s devolution intentions
[normal]. In addition, the short-term natu
[normal]re of funding competitions
[normal] present
[normal]s
[normal] challenges for local transport authorities in planning for the long-term and
